			<p>Lenke, 22, <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-822" type="subject">sister</term>. Now in <placeName
					ref="http://www.geonames.org/719819/hungary.html">Hungary</placeName>. Comes here in next days.</p>
			<p>Herman, 20, <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-822" type="subject">brother</term>. At present in same <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-278" type="subject">camp</term>.</p>
			<p>Etel, 19, <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-822" type="subject">sister</term>. At present in same <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-278" type="subject">camp</term>.</p>
			<p><term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-822" type="subject">Father's brother</term>: <persName
					ref="#ehri_et_weinstock_eugen">Eugen WEINSTOCK</persName>, <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/5128581/new-york-city.html">108
					Lewis st.</placeName>, <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/5128581/new-york-city.html">New York City</placeName>.</p>
			<p><term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-822" type="subject">Uncle</term> is trying to get <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1142" type="subject">affidavit</term> for all 4 <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-824" type="subject">children</term>.</p>
