			<p>Information obtained from:</p>
			<p><persName ref="#ehri_et_landau_bernat_bernard">Landau, Bernat</persName></p>

			<pb n="2" facs="EHRI-ET-YV4693907_02.jpg"/>
			<p>First displacement:</p>
			<p>April <date when="1944">1944</date> – left home with <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-822" type="subject"
					>mother</term> and <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-822" type="subject">brother</term> and <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-822" type="subject">sisters</term>.</p>
			<p>Chronological record.</p>
			<p><date when="1944-04">April 1944</date> left home with <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-822" type="subject"
					>mother</term>, <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-822" type="subject">brother</term> and <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-822" type="subject">sisters</term>. Went to <placeName
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-0" type="camp">Auschwitz Concentration camp</placeName>. <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-822" type="subject">Father</term> was taken to <placeName
					ref="http://www.geonames.org/719819/hungary.html">Hungarian</placeName>
				<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-508" type="subject">Labor Camp</term> in <date when="1942">1942</date>.
					<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-822" type="subject">Mother</term> was separated from <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-824" type="subject">children</term>. He and <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-822" type="subject">brother</term> went to <placeName
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-177" type="camp">Dachau</placeName> after 3 weeks.</p>
			<p><term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-822" type="subject">Sisters</term> went to <placeName
					ref="http://www.geonames.org/2879139/leipzig.html">Leipzig</placeName>.</p>
			<p>Then <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-822" type="subject">boys</term> to <placeName
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-252" type="camp">Allach</placeName>; <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-573" type="subject">liberated</term> there <date when="1945-05-01">May 1,
					1945</date>.</p>
			<p>Then went to <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/2927464/feldafing.html">Feldafing Camp</placeName> with <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-822" type="subject">brother</term>.</p>
			<p><term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-822" type="subject">Sisters</term> came to <placeName
					ref="http://www.geonames.org/2927464/feldafing.html">Feldafing</placeName>, arrived in <placeName
					ref="http://www.geonames.org/2806768/wolfratshausen.html">Wolfratshausen</placeName>.</p>
			<p><date when="1945-07">July 1945</date>.</p>
			<p>Lenke went home to <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-196" type="subject">look for parents</term>.</p>
			<p>Will come back. According to last <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-843" type="subject">letter</term> she
				did not find anybody there.</p>
			<p>Relatives</p>
			<p><term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-822" type="subject">Uncle</term><persName ref="#ehri_et_weinstock_eugen"
					>Eugen Weinstock</persName> in <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/5128581/new-york-city.html">New York City</placeName> will
				send <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1142" type="subject">affidavit</term> through <placeName
					ref="http://www.geonames.org/4140963/washington-d-c.html">Washington</placeName>. Contact made.</p>
			<p>Language</p>
			<p>Boy speaks Hungarian, German, Yiddish, Hebrew.</p>
			<p>Documents</p>
			<p>Certificate from <placeName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-177" type="camp">Concentration Camp
					Dachau</placeName>, dated <date when="1946-01-09">9 Jan. 1946</date>.</p>
			<p>School record</p>
